      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "### In-place Action Editing\r\nYou can now edit actions directly in the settings tab without navigating away or opening separate dialogs.\r\n<img width=\"500\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/67d631b7-5add-4435-84e6-4a906fc21838\"/>\r\n\r\n\r\n### Thinking Block Support\r\nAdded visual support for \"Thinking...\" blocks to better display reasoning processes from models that support it. Closes #72\r\n<img width=\"400\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/eccebd0a-4930-4c40-a0e9-00fec3eb0091\"/>\r\n\r\n### Asynchronous Parallel Execution\r\nActions can now run in parallel asynchronously, significantly improving performance when executing multiple tasks simultaneously (Closes #75).\r\n\r\n### Action Palette UI\r\nImproved contrast for better visibility and accessibility.\r\n\r\n### UI Separators\r\nEnhanced separator creation and rendering (fixed width and added support) for better list organization. Closes #88 \r\n<img width=\"500\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d971029a-20bb-4953-a800-540a14beaf3f\"/>",
