      "description": "### 🚨 Requires API v3 of AI Providers\r\nYou need to update your [AI Providers plugin](https://github.com/pfrankov/obsidian-ai-providers/) to the latest version to use this version of the plugin.\r\n\r\n### Added multilingual support\r\n<img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/5e5db60e-c4b7-4335-a4cd-6385ebe9c89c\" width=\"450\" alt=\"Languages Demo\"/>\r\n\r\n- English\r\n- Chinese\r\n- German\r\n- Russian\r\n\r\nCreate PR if it's not translated correctly to your language or you want to add a new one.\r\n\r\n### Moved ✨ Enhanced Action (RAG) to AI Providers\r\n- Means that embeddings will now be calculated only once for every provider/model pair and then will be shared between the plugins that use [AI Providers](https://github.com/pfrankov/obsidian-ai-providers/).\r\n- 🚨 It also means that old embeddings created before this update must be recalculated.",
